""SELECT t.\"FarmId\", (
    SELECT f.\"Name\"
    FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0
    INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
    WHERE t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"FarmId\" = t0.\"FarmId\"
    LIMIT 1) AS \"FarmName\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TotalHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalPlanned\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TilledHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalTilled\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t3.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0)
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\""

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT l.\"FieldId\", f1.\"Id\", f1.\"CreatedDate\", f1.\"CreatorId\", f1.\"Deleted\", f1.\"Description\", f1.\"FarmId\", f1.\"Irrigation\", f1.\"IsActive\", f1.\"IsArchived\", f1.\"ModifiedBy\", f1.\"Name\", f1.\"Size\", f1.\"SoilType\", f1.\"UpdatedAt\", f1.\"Version\", l.\"Label\", l.\"Longitude\", l.\"Latitude\", l.\"Altitude\", l.\"Id\" AS \"Id0\", l.\"UpdatedAt\" AS \"UpdatedAt0\", l.\"Deleted\" AS \"Deleted0\", l.\"CreatedDate\" AS \"CreatedDate0\", l.\"CreatorId\" AS \"CreatorId0\", l.\"ModifiedBy\" AS \"ModifiedBy0\", l.\"IsArchived\" AS \"IsArchived0\", l.\"IsActive\" AS \"IsActive0\"

FROM (
    SELECT f.\"Id\", f.\"Name\", f.\"Size\", f.\"Arable\", f.\"Cleared\", f.\"Terrain\", f.\"Latitude\", f.\"Longitude\", f.\"SoilType\", f.\"UpdatedAt\", f.\"Deleted\", f.\"CreatedDate\", f.\"CreatorId\", f.\"ModifiedBy\", f.\"IsArchived\", f.\"IsActive\"

) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0.\"Name\", f0.\"Description\", f0.\"SoilType\", f0.\"Irrigation\", f0.\"Size\", f0.\"FarmId\", f1.\"Name\" AS \"Name0\", f0.\"Id\", f1.\"Id\" AS \"Id0\", t1.\"FieldId\", t1.\"Id\" AS \"Id1\", t1.\"CreatedDate\", t1.\"CreatorId\", t1.\"Deleted\", t1.\"Description\" AS \"Description0\", t1.\"FarmId\" AS \"FarmId0\", t1.\"Irrigation\" AS \"Irrigation0\", t1.\"IsActive\", t1.\"IsArchived\", t1.\"ModifiedBy\", t1.\"Name\" AS \"Name1\", t1.\"Size\" AS \"Size0\", t1.\"SoilType\" AS \"SoilType0\", t1.\"UpdatedAt\", t1.\"Version\", t1.\"Label\", t1.\"Longitude\", t1.\"Latitude\", t1.\"Altitude\", t1.\"Id0\" AS \"Id00\", t1.\"UpdatedAt0\", t1.\"Deleted0\", t1.\"CreatedDate0\", t1.\"CreatorId0\", t1.\"ModifiedBy0\", t1.\"IsArchived0\", t1.\"IsActive0\", f0.\"UpdatedAt\" AS \"UpdatedAt1\", f0.\"Deleted\" AS \"Deleted1\", f0.\"CreatedDate\" AS \"CreatedDate1\", f0.\"CreatorId\" AS \"CreatorId1\", f0.\"ModifiedBy\" AS \"ModifiedBy1\", f0.\"IsArchived\" AS \"IsArchived1\", f0.\"IsActive\" AS \"IsActive1\"
    FROM \"Fields\" AS f0
    INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f1 ON f0.\"FarmId\" = f1.\"Id\"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT l.\"FieldId\", f2.\"Id\", f2.\"CreatedDate\", f2.\"CreatorId\", f2.\"Deleted\", f2.\"Description\", f2.\"FarmId\", f2.\"Irrigation\", f2.\"IsActive\", f2.\"IsArchived\", f2.\"ModifiedBy\", f2.\"Name\", f2.\"Size\", f2.\"SoilType\", f2.\"UpdatedAt\", f2.\"Version\", l.\"Label\", l.\"Longitude\", l.\"Latitude\", l.\"Altitude\", l.\"Id\" AS \"Id0\", l.\"UpdatedAt\" AS \"UpdatedAt0\", l.\"Deleted\" AS \"Deleted0\", l.\"CreatedDate\" AS \"CreatedDate0\", l.\"CreatorId\" AS \"CreatorId0\", l.\"ModifiedBy\" AS \"ModifiedBy0\", l.\"IsArchived\" AS \"IsArchived0\", l.\"IsActive\" AS \"IsActive0\"
        FROM \"Locations\" AS l
        INNER JOIN \"Fields\" AS f2 ON l.\"FieldId\" = f2.\"Id\"
        WHERE l.\"Discriminator\" = 'FieldLocation'
    ) AS t1 ON f0.\"Id\" = t1.\"FieldId\"
) AS t0 ON t.\"Id\" = t0.\"FarmId\"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT l0.\"Longitude\", l0.\"Latitude\", l0.\"Id\", l0.\"CreatedDate\", l0.\"FarmLocation_FarmId\"
    FROM \"Locations\" AS l0
    WHERE l0.\"Discriminator\" = 'FarmLocation'
) AS t2 ON t.\"Id\" = t2.\"FarmLocation_FarmId\"
ORDER BY t.\"Id\", t0.\"Id\", t0.\"Id0\", t0.\"CreatedDate0\", t0.\"Id00\", t0.\"Id1\", t2.\"CreatedDate\""

) AS t0 ON t.\"Id\" = t0.\"FarmId\"

INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON f.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT l.\"FieldId\", f1.\"Id\", f1.\"CreatedDate\", f1.\"CreatorId\", f1.\"Deleted\", f1.\"Description\", f1.\"FarmId\", f1.\"Irrigation\", f1.\"IsActive\", f1.\"IsArchived\", f1.\"ModifiedBy\", f1.\"Name\", f1.\"Size\", f1.\"SoilType\", f1.\"UpdatedAt\", f1.\"Version\", l.\"Label\", l.\"Longitude\", l.\"Latitude\", l.\"Altitude\", l.\"Id\" AS \"Id0\", l.\"UpdatedAt\" AS \"UpdatedAt0\", l.\"Deleted\" AS \"Deleted0\", l.\"CreatedDate\" AS \"CreatedDate0\", l.\"CreatorId\" AS \"CreatorId0\", l.\"ModifiedBy\" AS \"ModifiedBy0\", l.\"IsArchived\" AS \"IsArchived0\", l.\"IsActive\" AS \"IsActive0\"

""SELECT f.\"Name\", f.\"Description\", f.\"SoilType\", f.\"Irrigation\", f.\"Size\", f.\"FarmId\", f0.\"Name\", f.\"Id\", f0.\"Id\", t.\"FieldId\", t.\"Id\", t.\"CreatedDate\", t.\"CreatorId\", t.\"Deleted\", t.\"Description\", t.\"FarmId\", t.\"Irrigation\", t.\"IsActive\", t.\"IsArchived\", t.\"ModifiedBy\", t.\"Name\", t.\"Size\", t.\"SoilType\", t.\"UpdatedAt\", t.\"Version\", t.\"Label\", t.\"Longitude\", t.\"Latitude\", t.\"Altitude\", t.\"Id0\", t.\"UpdatedAt0\", t.\"Deleted0\", t.\"CreatedDate0\", t.\"CreatorId0\", t.\"ModifiedBy0\", t.\"IsArchived0\", t.\"IsActive0\", f.\"UpdatedAt\", f.\"Deleted\", f.\"CreatedDate\", f.\"CreatorId\", f.\"ModifiedBy\", f.\"IsArchived\", f.\"IsActive\"

INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON f.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT l.\"FieldId\", f1.\"Id\", f1.\"CreatedDate\", f1.\"CreatorId\", f1.\"Deleted\", f1.\"Description\", f1.\"FarmId\", f1.\"Irrigation\", f1.\"IsActive\", f1.\"IsArchived\", f1.\"ModifiedBy\", f1.\"Name\", f1.\"Size\", f1.\"SoilType\", f1.\"UpdatedAt\", f1.\"Version\", l.\"Label\", l.\"Longitude\", l.\"Latitude\", l.\"Altitude\", l.\"Id\" AS \"Id0\", l.\"UpdatedAt\" AS \"UpdatedAt0\", l.\"Deleted\" AS \"Deleted0\", l.\"CreatedDate\" AS \"CreatedDate0\", l.\"CreatorId\" AS \"CreatorId0\", l.\"ModifiedBy\" AS \"ModifiedBy0\", l.\"IsArchived\" AS \"IsArchived0\", l.\"IsActive\" AS \"IsActive0\"

    INNER JOIN \"Fields\" AS f1 ON l.\"FieldId\" = f1.\"Id\"
